, {"id": 37, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那還真是抱歉啊。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bdevilmgc", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$p_skill_darkholespell", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_explosion_stone", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 50.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 100.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1125_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.9, "bend": 1.0, "afrom": 0.7, "ato": 0.7, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1126_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.9, "bend": 1.0, "afrom": 0.7, "ato": 0.7, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你現在想要一起去迎接陛下嗎？還是企圖阻止陛下重新降臨塵世？", "name": "“巫王的餘音”？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1125_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒有資格，也做不到。", "name": "“巫王的餘音”？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1125_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早該想到的，我們早該想到的。", "name": "“巫王的餘音”？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1125_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明明陛下的血脈如此強大，精神如此堅韌，而塵世之音不過是其樂聲的萬一，卻已經讓你痛苦到難以承受。", "name": "“巫王的餘音”？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1125_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你生來孱弱，孱弱得背負不起任何期待。", "name": "“巫王的餘音”？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1125_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位的意思是，你們將這些毫無價值的雜音強塞進我的腦海……", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到頭來，我應該為這件事負責？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1125_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.9, "bend": 1.0, "afrom": 0.7, "ato": 0.7, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1126_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.9, "bend": 1.0, "afrom": 0.7, "ato": 0.7, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，你應該慶幸，黑鍵。", "name": "“巫王的餘音”？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果一開始就知曉塵世之音並非獲取陛下遺產的鑰匙，那對雙子會假模假樣地賞賜你烏提卡家族的封地嗎？", "name": "“巫王的餘音”？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不。甚至等不到那時候，你就會死在繈褓之中。", "name": "“巫王的餘音”？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“烏提卡伯爵”，你應以享有這個封號為榮，更應以享有這個封號為恥！", "name": "“巫王的餘音”？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，我也這麼想。", "name": "黑鍵"}, 