me", "attributes": {"content": "多少人因巫王的暴政橫死，多少人不明不白地消失，萊塔尼亞遍體鱗傷，二十三年過去，有些傷口依舊在流血。", "name": "憤怒的路人？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1125_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*萊塔尼亞粗口*！結果那個暴君悄無聲息地死在了一個夜晚，甚至沒有得到任何應有的懲罰！", "name": "憤怒的路人？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1125_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而你是他在這個世上唯一的後裔，你生來就帶著罪孽的血腥味，你該代他贖罪！代他向整個萊塔尼亞懺悔！", "name": "憤怒的路人？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1125_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑鍵，你有什麼資格，一邊過著養尊處優的生活，一邊自嘲著“自己明明誰也不是”？", "name": "憤怒的路人？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1125_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和你們一樣，沒有一天不在痛恨這罪孽的血！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1125_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.9, "bend": 1.0, "afrom": 0.7, "ato": 0.7, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，你壓根不清楚它到底引誘了多少罪惡！那些殘黨一次次潛入烏提卡領，圍著你的高塔打轉，像嗅到了腐肉的蒼蠅。", "name": "烏提卡領民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1125_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的小兒子才剛進治安隊當差，就因為發現了他們的蹤跡，屍體在水溝裡漂了三天才被發現。而你永遠躲在高塔上！", "name": "烏提卡領民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1125_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你甚至不知道烏提卡領到底有多大，出產什麼作物，首都的稅務官一年來幾趟，這幾年領地又遭受了什麼災害。", "name": "烏提卡領民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1125_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有比你更可恨的領主，伯爵大人。", "name": "烏提卡領民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1125_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1125_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_498_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.9, "bend": 1.0, "afrom": 0.7, "ato": 0.7, "focus": "n", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.9, "bend": 1.0, "afrom": 0.7, "ato": 0.7, "focus": "l", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$p_skill_darkholeborn", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_smkedspte", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.9, "bend": 1.0, "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.7, "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "停下來，別再往前了。現在的你，越英勇越像個笑話。", "name": "別格勒？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑鍵，你如此可悲。", "name": "別格勒？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還記得格特魯德嗎？她死前曾留下最惡毒的詛咒，詛咒維謝海姆、詛咒萊塔尼亞、詛咒巫王……她也詛咒了你。", "name": "別格勒？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她詛咒你“永遠無法擺脫血脈中的瘋狂”。", "name": "別格勒？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你回到崔林特爾梅的時候，我在想，該死，這個瘋女人的詛咒真的應驗了，倔強的孩子終究無法掙脫命運的漩渦。", "name": "別格勒？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他當然不會順應命運，但這一次，他無可避免地要為掙脫它而陷入瘋狂。", "name": "別格勒？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你應該感到輕鬆，不是嗎？", "name": "別格勒？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塵世之音困擾了你十多年，與其說你一直在竭力抵抗，不如說你在小心翼翼地看守著它。", "name": "別格勒？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "守著一枚炸彈，害怕它隨時會被引爆，害怕它被有心之人利用，戕害到無辜的生命。", "name": "別格勒？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是你沉重但意義非凡的……命運。", "name": "別格勒？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可既然它只是雜音，只是並不致命的頭痛……回去吧，黑鍵。格特魯德的詛咒失敗了。", "name": "別格勒？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不能接受！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.9, "bend": 1.0, "afrom": 0.7, "ato": 0.7, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為這是一種更加殘忍的詛咒？", "name": "別格勒？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到頭來，你的努力不值一提，你的反抗毫無意義。那些為此而犧牲的人，那些你決定永生銘記的眼淚和笑容……", "name": "別格勒？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要如何去面對？", "name": "別格勒？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你突然發現，信任、憐惜、理解、彼此託付……那些無比美好的情感，原來並不因稀少而珍貴。", "name": "別格勒？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們一下子變得輕飄飄的……", "name": "別格勒？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像是一個玩笑。", "name": "別格勒？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "是啊，玩笑。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "它們怎麼能，只是一個玩笑？！", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_486_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.9, "bend": 1.0, "afrom": 0.7, "ato": 0.7, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$p_skill_darkholeboost", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_smkedspte", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#5$1", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g11_thronesworld", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dimnlspamb", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.5, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他看見了高塔。"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，果然。我知道你就在裡面。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕死去了這麼久，你還是妄想讓這座邪惡的高塔重新降臨在萊塔尼亞。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不會得逞！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會施展所有的法術，我會揮動法杖直至它折斷，我會運轉源石骰子直至它碎成齏粉。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你還有血肉，我就摧毀你的血肉。如果你還有魂靈，我就湮滅你的魂靈。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要質問你詛咒你唾駡你，我要殺死你。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——巫王！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.5, "fillto": 0.15, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.5, "fillto": 0.15, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_act29side_sys_intro", "key": "$m_act29side_sys_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "44_i12_1", "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3, "y": 300.0, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xTo": 200.0, "duration": 35.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "弗朗茨。", "name": "巫王"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別去碰空氣中的音符。", "name": "巫王"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被我刪去的這部分旋律，其中融合的術式在完全逸散前仍有可怕的力量。", "name": "巫王"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "平復你的情緒，迴避千年前先賢們的意志，別讓自己的心神被牽引……", "name": "巫王"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "44_i12_1", "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3, "x": 400.0, "y": 100.0, "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xTo": 0.0, "duration": 40.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑鍵攥緊法杖，但他說不出哪怕一個字。"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他曾讀過所有關於巫王的文獻，甚至不久前還被囚禁在這個房間，他當然知曉這段歷史。"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "音符在房間內緩緩流淌，名為“敘拉古”的旋律正在離開“萊塔尼亞”的大樂章。"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他彷彿聽見了巨大的雷、連綿的雨和浩蕩的風，“萊塔尼亞的意志”化作與天地等同的偉力，反覆沖刷著這個不大的房間。"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "僅僅站在門口，澎湃的能量便死死壓住了他的心跳。"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.15, "fillto": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.15, "fillto": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "44_i12_1", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 10.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "房間中央的人並未回頭看他，那個人是如此專注，又是如此傲然。驚濤駭浪中，他是那塊永遠高出浪頭的礁石。"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑鍵不由得懷疑自己來錯了地方，這裡彷彿是某個作曲家宿命的夜晚，或者歷史學者最激昂的課堂。"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡沒有他的仇，沒有他的命，他的憤怒無地自容。"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑鍵突然意識到一件事：他回想過往的全部人生，哪怕在那些最為恐怖的噩夢裡——"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自己其實從未真正見過巫王。"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g7_ludwigsuniv_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "弗萊蒙特，你又遲到了。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不記得你是個受歡迎的老師，你也會被學生圍住沒辦法脫身嗎？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#1$2", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#1$2"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第一，如果因施教者的脾氣而在知識面前卻步，說明這群號稱萊塔尼亞最優秀的年輕人日後也只配替高塔清清苔蘚。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#1$2"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第二，每個月給我發放學者津貼的是路德維格大學，所以我似乎沒有必要被你召之即來。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#1$2"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#9$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是不是不該跟赫爾昏佐倫陛下頂嘴？", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#9$2"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2", "duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也不是第一次了。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下個月，各大區的選帝侯便會陸續到達維杜尼亞，我們剩的時間不多，弗萊蒙特。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我希望他們覲見結束時，能將更新之後的金律樂章副本帶回各自的大區。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#9$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你已經是那些鹿和羊口中千年一遇的明君了，就這麼急著鞏固自己的威信？", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#9$2"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下一步是什麼，將選帝侯們的軍隊和行政權力收歸宮廷的高塔？", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#9$2"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們討論過這個問題。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛到萊塔尼亞那時候，當時的皇帝就在頭疼敘拉古的問題。這都過去多久了？", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#1$2"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些狼崽子們如今也只敢搞些大一點的小動作。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#1$2"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你才剛剛即位，不如多花點時間挑挑大典上要穿的華服。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#1$2"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "挑好了。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#8$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#8$2"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#7$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你仍在擔心，改寫金律樂章，以及後續的一系列國策，可能會讓整個國家陷入不可知的動亂？", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#7$2"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#5$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並不關心萊塔尼亞，但帶著圖書館到處搬家確實很麻煩。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#5$2"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從當上恩瓦德大區選帝侯開始，你就在研究這樂章，我們都清楚它到底是怎麼回事，為什麼千年來，沒人想過也沒人能修改它。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#5$2"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#6$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "將三大篇章、十重旋律編織成一體的，與其說是音樂的動機或主題，不如說是千年前那些源石技藝大師融合而成的超級術式……", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#6$2"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是萊塔尼亞創建之初，無數先賢對這個國家的偉大創造、思考與護佑。是“萊塔尼亞的無上意志”。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#6$2"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#5$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它無限接近於永恆。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#5$2"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“永恆”？", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了米諾斯那幫喜歡在白牆下討論“人能否兩次踏入同一條河流”的哲學家，恐怕只有巫妖才喜歡用這個詞。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也唯有你們才理解這個詞的含義。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#6$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“永恆”——不更不易，不移不改。但永恆不等於不朽。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#6$2"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誠然，構建樂章的先賢們在千年前完成了難以企及的偉業。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#6$2"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“萊塔尼亞”從那時成為這個國家的名，又不僅是國家的名。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#6$2"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“萊塔尼亞”讓這片土地上的萬民共榮辱，“萊塔尼亞”將典雅、和諧、道德與美鐫刻在了我們的每一次呼吸。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#6$2"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們在千年之前就對這個國度做出了最優的展望與規劃，他們讓“萊塔尼亞”成了這片土地上的真理。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#6$2"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但所有的真理都會朽壞，敘拉古的離心離德便是最好的證明。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#3$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我，將為萊塔尼亞帶來一個更好的未來。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#3$2"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊塔尼亞的新君主取出懷中的樂章，側頭看向巫妖。"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“永恆”、“不朽”……"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫爾昏佐倫說話的聲音並不重，但弗萊蒙特清晰地聽見這些宏大的詞語在他唇齒間破碎、重組。"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#4$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#9$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很狂妄，很“赫爾昏佐倫”。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#9$2"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#5$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你如何保證，萊塔尼亞在你手中不會遭遇更大的危機，你所謂的未來能夠不朽？", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#5$2"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有樂章不可被改寫，沒有法術不可被超越，沒有意志不可被戰勝，沒有未知不可被征服……", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#5$2"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不朽，在於“更新”。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時至今日，海洋與天空仍被籠罩在認知的迷霧中，大地便是泰拉人所感所知的極限。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#3$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可根據你分享的知識，連最高的雲層、最深的海底，也不過是被時間與空間囚禁的“實在”。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#3$2"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而在實在之外，存在著世界的另一面，虛無、詭譎而危險的未知之境。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#3$2"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如若問題無盡，說明答案無盡。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#4$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "烏提卡的伯爵塔過於矮小，所以我在維杜尼亞建起始源之塔，它已是萊塔尼亞最高的建築。但未必是整片大地最高的建築……", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#4$2"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我永不停止，這是我與歷代先賢的區別。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#4$2"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是我的“不朽”，弗萊蒙特。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#9$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望你再建一座新塔的時候，房間能多些，這樣不至於修改一份樂章還要借用我的密室。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#9$2"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#9$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "會的。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#9$2"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#1$2"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，我們開始吧。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#8$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我去把所有的共振捕捉裝置打開，待會拆解旋律的時候，能看得更清晰一些。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#8$2"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_mgcdevcstartp", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_scroll", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫爾昏佐倫在房間中央的椅子上坐穩，淩空鋪開樂章，弗萊蒙特則連踢帶拽地將各種珍貴的古籍挪至一邊，為術式矩陣空出位置。"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#8$2", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，弗萊蒙特，你們如何稱呼世界的另一面來著？", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（薩卡茲語）“千絲萬弦之始終”。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#1$2"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很小器的名字。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“命結”的存在讓巫妖這個種族獲得了幾乎是最為特殊的能力。藏好命結，意味著你們擁有永不終結的生命。", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#8$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巫妖得以在無限的時間裡窺見世界的無限真相，卻只是將它們作為知識的一頁？", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#8$2"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謹慎是我們的天性。發現越多，宜居的地方越少。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#1$2"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，弗萊蒙特，你呢？", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#2$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我？", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#2$2"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#4$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“千絲萬弦之始終”……", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#4$2"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你時常抱怨手底下那些巫妖不是還年輕就是太呆板，卻也只是將那個空間當成藏自己命結的抽屜，沒想著進去看看？", "name": "赫爾昏佐倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$2"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "44_i12_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_golden_star_01", "layer": 0.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_golden_melody_01", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_golden_melody_02", "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巨大的寒意席捲弗萊蒙特全身。"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "微小但耀眼的光芒在赫爾昏佐倫法杖的頂端綻開，他已經開始演奏金律樂章，弗萊蒙特手上的動作也未停止。"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巫妖與卡普里尼，王庭之主與萊塔尼亞皇帝，一直如此默契。"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再緊張的時刻，兩人也能見縫插針討論幾個問題，哲學、音樂，有時候是萊塔尼亞的氣候與飲食。"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫爾昏佐倫就是如此自然地提到了這件事，提到了真正威脅巫妖生死的，秘密。"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倘若盡全力施展“放逐”，命弦是否能在一瞬間消解所有音符，將面前這個毫不設防的傢伙湮滅在虛空之中？"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無人知曉萊塔尼亞的新皇帝來到了這裡，他有足夠的時間知會巫妖王庭從這個國家撤離。"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但赫爾昏佐倫就是如此自然地提到了這件事，提到了漫長歲月裡從來無人發現的，秘密。"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈——", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "良久，弗萊蒙特放聲大笑。"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正好，對那個空間的研究我也碰到了一些瓶頸。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫爾昏佐倫，你要是真的感興趣……", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以把命結借給你。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magicchange", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "差不多得了，赫爾昏佐倫。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不覺得懷舊很倒胃口嗎，讓人想把隔夜飯都吐出來。更何況我還趕時間。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g15_kingsthrone", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_churchfire", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "b"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.5, "channel": "b", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好久不見，弗萊蒙特。", "name": "巫王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1116_1#1$1"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你還記得從我這借走了什麼，還回來吧。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#7$1"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "b", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}